454
00:37:13,495 --> 00:37:15,486
Let's go.

455
00:37:26,108 --> 00:37:28,076
Phil, why don't
you test your headset?

456
00:37:28,143 --> 00:37:30,703
Check, one, two.

457
00:37:34,749 --> 00:37:37,377
So, where shall we set up?

458
00:37:38,453 --> 00:37:40,683
Over here.

459
00:37:40,755 --> 00:37:44,657
We can cover the door,
stay in the shadows.

460
00:37:46,495 --> 00:37:49,589
Uh, Jarod.
Something doesn't feel right about this.

461
00:37:49,664 --> 00:37:51,894
Well, it's a pretty scary place.

462
00:37:51,967 --> 00:37:54,834
That and the fact that Ken Watanabe
