You're fired.

545
00:42:45,560 --> 00:42:48,085
[All Murmuring]

546
00:43:12,153 --> 00:43:14,485
<i>Oh, my God.</i>

547
00:43:26,201 --> 00:43:28,931
Miss Parker! Sydney!

548
00:43:31,406 --> 00:43:35,137
- It can't be.
- Sydney! Miss P.!

549
00:43:35,210 --> 00:43:39,943
- Broots! You moron!
- <i>Miss Parker.!</i>

550
00:43:40,014 --> 00:43:42,414
<i>Down here.!</i>

551
00:43:44,052 --> 00:43:46,316
Sydney, wake up.

552
00:43:51,860 --> 00:43:53,851
[Chattering]

553
00:43:56,431 --> 00:43:58,365
Hi.

554
00:43:58,433 --> 00:44:00,993
How're you doing?
I figured you guys might be hungry.

555
00:44:01,069 --> 00:44:03,469
Forget that.
Does anybody smoke? Smoke?

556
00:44:03,538 --> 00:44:05,529
- No.
- No.

557
00:44:08,810 --> 00:44:12,109
Hi. Uh, can l...

558
00:44:12,180 --> 00:44:14,171
Thank you.

559
00:44:27,462 --> 00:44:30,556
Boy, it's lucky
I found you guys.

560
00:44:30,632 --> 00:44:32,566
Otherwise, you would've been toast.

561
00:44:35,370 --> 00:44:39,704
<i>You can put any fantasy about me</i>
<i>thanking you to rest, Broots.</i>

562
00:44:39,774 --> 00:44:41,708
[Huffs]

563
00:44:41,776 --> 00:44:44,176
Right.
[Chuckles]

564
00:44:44,245 --> 00:44:48,375
So, what did you guys
talk about all this time?

565
00:44:50,552 --> 00:44:52,986
Nothing.

566
00:44:53,054 --> 00:44:55,045
<i>Nothing at all.</i>

567
00:44:59,227 --> 00:45:01,821
[Huffs]
You're welcome.

568
00:45:08,336 --> 00:45:11,999
This is great.
I don't know how to thank you.

569
00:45:12,073 --> 00:45:14,439
- <i>I mean, you built this harness for me...</i>
- [Chuckling]

570
00:45:14,509 --> 00:45:16,534
<i>and got me myjob back</i>
<i>at the station.</i>

571
00:45:16,611 --> 00:45:19,045
You've got to promise me that
this will never make the air.

572
00:45:19,113 --> 00:45:20,876
I promise.

573
00:45:20,949 --> 00:45:26,251
Well, you're gonna have to
send me the video.

574
00:45:26,321 --> 00:45:31,384
- That's what you do, isn't it?
- Yeah, it is.

575
00:45:35,530 --> 00:45:38,192
- Good luck, huh?
- Take care.

576
00:45:46,908 --> 00:45:49,376
